{"tid":769254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"會計界梁繼昌關注AI「搶飯碗」  - 港聞","createTime":"2018-08-06T04:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T05:14:25.000Z","uid":72280,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0c02ae460291db6550ad61b126c1dc447130a3ee","tid":769254,"uid":72280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:47:17.000Z","msg":"會計界梁繼昌關注AI「搶飯碗」  - 港聞<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】人工智能（AI）普及，開始同人類爭飯碗，專業人士會否都有被取代嘅危機？會計界立法會議員梁繼昌（Kenneth）同Emily講，外國會計界嘅AI應用都幾普遍，例如審計工作，以前做併購盡職審查，要整理成千上萬嘅法律文件去確認各項條款，就算十幾個員工都要用差唔多半年，但今時今日AI有自然語言處理（natural-language processing），就可以消化文件條文，6至8人團隊唔使一個月就搞掂，佢仲聽聞香港會計界Big Four公司都有研究AI應用。<br />\n<br />\n咁人類以後咪無碇企？Kenneth就話部分會計師工作例如稅務規劃同策略發展，都要靠人類度橋獻計嘅，但就希望政府成日話大搞創科，都要諗吓專業人才培圳要轉型，除咗本行專業知識，都要識吓科技，以免被淘汰。Kenneth話星期六會搞個研討會，請嚟創科局長楊偉雄等，傾吓AI對業界嘅衝擊，順便同業界交流。"},{"pid":"966c2823168869ed79ca5dad025c0499ce5ca3f0","tid":769254,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:48:22.000Z","msg":"用金碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7dac265093b6598f392b1fa45d49aaf7296ffae","tid":769254,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:50:28.000Z","msg":"鐵飯碗molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2df008784f4841dc4068fc736cf748df15829427","tid":769254,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7dac265093b6598f392b1fa45d49aaf7296ffae","tid":769254,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:50:28.000Z","msg":"鐵飯碗molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:00:45.000Z","msg":"邊有人講過Audit 係鐵飯碗,<br />\n從來都係Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13bb382b7442b7af027503ed42d1b4f45a01c0f9","tid":769254,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:02:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"401f4f4ca4ea6f62aaf68dbdf682424d9e7deef7","tid":769254,"uid":72280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2df008784f4841dc4068fc736cf748df15829427","tid":769254,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7dac265093b6598f392b1fa45d49aaf7296ffae","tid":769254,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T04:50:28.000Z","msg":"鐵飯碗molamola<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:00:45.000Z","msg":"邊有人講過Audit 係鐵飯碗,<br />\n從來都係Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:04:10.000Z","msg":"對manager 黎講<br />\nD audit 囡都是condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4260b48746bb37f0b592ed1f05b007db0b47031","tid":769254,"uid":130438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"ai發展夠成熟既話的確係可以取代大部分人手<br />\n例如醫生 護士 律師 <br />\n起碼減少左人手需求"},{"pid":"7576ea2ece43fef2cf66ba6ae4ca94648d39f9d0","tid":769254,"uid":131691,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T05:14:25.000Z","msg":"唔止會計<br />\n過往以爲不能取代嘅精英職業外國都已經用AI玩緊<br />\n律師處理文件AI快過一team人<br />\n醫生做diagnosis甚至medication都已經係AI assisted<br />\n<br />\n真正不能取代嘅反而係啲「感性」，好難量化嘅專業<br />\n例如傳統廚藝，古典音樂，話劇，棟篤笑，舞蹈"}]}